{"tid":2043252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯駐美大使館發表聲明 關注明州暴動 呼籲美國會公平調查及人權組織監察美國對此事行動","createTime":"2020-05-30T09:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T12:02:44.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a12c1136b89d8c06852df00b67d4f0021c4ff5c7","tid":2043252,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T09:50:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20200530/0/1/2/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%A7%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A4%A8%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-11728577.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20200530%2F0%2F1%2F2%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%25A7%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-11728577.html&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypD3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=09ab5e32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sina.com.hk/news/article/20200530/0/1/2/%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E9%A7%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A4%A8%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-11728577.html</a><br />\n#俄羅斯駐美大使館發聲明#】俄羅斯駐美大使館在臉書上發表聲明，稱對發生在明尼阿波利斯的黑人男子喬治&middot;弗洛伊德死亡而引發的暴亂表示關注，希望美國當局會公正調查，為媒體運行提供公正的安全的正常環境。我們也會密切關注國際人權組織對此事的反應，期望他們在對事件評估時採用不偏不倚的方式。同時，我們建議俄羅斯同胞不要前往相關危險區域。"},{"pid":"a30dd2d0b6834854118491e4234f8131f1982c13","tid":2043252,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T10:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f344dc5787ed1e6e8929653620ee8db26ac3ae1","tid":2043252,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T12:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}